entry.string: The same registered ID (#(1)) was found belonging to a #(2) module in the file system and a registered #(3) module in the database. Please correct this and regenerate the list.
entry.translation: ID berdaftar (#(1)) yang sama kepunyaan suatu modul #(2) dijumpai dalam sistem fail dan suatu modul berdaftar #(3) dalam pangkalan data. Sila betulkan dan jana semula senarai tersebut.

entry.string: The module #(1) is found with two different registered IDs, #(2) in the file system and #(3) in the database. Please correct this and regenerate the list.
entry.translation: Modul #(1) dijumpai dengan dua ID berdaftar, #(2), berbeza dalam sistem fail dan #(3) dalam pangkalan data. Sila betulkan dan jana semula senarai tersebut.
